                <head>Valley Railroad</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The paper argues that Augusta cannot rely on Baltimore to build the Valley
                    Railroad. They are already in danger of losing the aid of Rockbridge. If the
                    county does not act, the two former places will decide on a road that does not
                    go through Staunton.</summary>
